{"tid":1739622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黎明行動] 行動指南討論區 - 唔好再推太多空泛post","createTime":"2019-11-19T15:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T16:13:15.000Z","uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cae2b1aeaf1702297cca0c89416e4a426db69656","tid":1739622,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:55:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">拿拿林出完個post就訓，聽朝起身食頭圍封路</span><br />\n<br />\n見到好多手足唔夠人，又唔夠資源封路<br />\n希望大家記住，唔夠人又冇資源嘅話，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">封淨一條線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解? 因為班懶鳩廢中只要行到車，就唔會落車清rb<br />\n人手夠資源夠，梗係個rb封死條路啦<br />\n但唔夠資源嘅話，勉強封死晒，只會激發廢中廢老落車清rb，對件事冇咩幫助<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><ins>咁點樣封淨一條線呀?</ins></em></span><br />\n詳情參考巴打嘅post啦!<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動 - rb封淨一條線比全封效益更大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1707876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1707876</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔講，訓先，聽朝見喇大家!!!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">記住除咗封路仲要塞鐵</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">同埋我覺得唔使4點半咁早，嚇走晒啲人，6點係個合理時間</span><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n有咩新結果都開個新post整合推上去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7tgeSsv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7tgeSsv.png&h=100ea111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/19/235339_fe60688fe4a8ed994a535fd2848fa0d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F19%2F235339_fe60688fe4a8ed994a535fd2848fa0d5.png&h=3ae2948d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arYtcsx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarYtcsx.jpg&h=fda698e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d80094d676327cb52dad7a85b91a1f9956cec22","tid":1739622,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2504972b